{"tid":1188282,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"鄭裕玲向攝影大師陸永取經學影相　照片失焦Do姐揶揄：Focus要放後面","createTime":"2019-06-06T07:11:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-06T11:21:44.000Z","uid":130626,"like":20,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"13e5cbf5746aa305893126da2c9300f4894ce969","tid":1188282,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T07:11:23.000Z","msg":"鄭裕玲（Do姐）與農夫的陸永及C君因合作電視節目而變成「好拍檔」，近日Do姐與農夫為新節目《Do姐晚間看地球》再度出埠，Do姐本想向「攝影大師」陸永學攝影技巧，怎料對方影出out foucs的照片，要Do姐發文諷刺陸永：「這樣才有朦朧美！」<br />\n<br />\n其實陸永去年為慶祝太太生日，特地買相機和報讀影相課程，以便為太太和兩位女兒影更多靚相。<br />\n所以Do姐鄭裕玲與陸永出埠為新節目《Do姐晚間看地球》拍攝時，愛靚的Do姐得知陸永對攝影布研究，於是特意向對方請教。<br />\n怎料「陸大師」的作品與Do姐所認知的「攝影大作」有很大出入，Do姐昨晚（6月5日）在個人IG帖文，首先是多張陸永手把手親自教Do姐攝影的照片：<br />\n&quot;我想影多D靚相同大家分享，但因本人攝影技術有限，好彩同行有學過攝影的陸永。我請求陸大師指點，陸大師也悉心教導，循循善誘。&quot;<br />\n<br />\n可是Do姐上載的最後一張照片，只見坐在前方的她完全out foucs的，而身後的景物清晰無比，拍出「前朦後清」的照片，Do姐在文中取笑陸永的攝影技術：<br />\n&quot;最後那張照片便是陸大師的作品。原來我呢世人都唔識影相！Focus 是要放在後面的，這樣相中人才有朦朧美！此種攝影方式相當難掌握，本人正在努力學習中！在此多謝陸大師賜教！&quot;<br />\n<br />\n曾經跟農夫和Do姐出埠的黃翠如留言讚陸永「好叻」，不少網民亦大讚Do姐幽默感十足。<br />\n雖然Do姐喜歡罵農夫與他們鬥嘴，但其實她非常疼愛二人，甚至愛屋及烏，知道陸永的女兒Hannah陸一穎，跟她一樣喜歡韓國偶像團體BTS，更將一票難求的演唱會門票轉贈其女Hannah，一同去追星！<br />\n<img src=\"https://topick.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2370000/2370559/DO_thumb_20190606_ch_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2370000%2F2370559%2FDO_thumb_20190606_ch_1024.jpg&h=076c4190&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://topick.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2370000/2370559/60796076_1025154061012172_4148192100862638215_n_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2370000%2F2370559%2F60796076_1025154061012172_4148192100862638215_n_1024.jpg&h=22e5593d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://topick.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2370000/2370559/61858897_351734252193627_1680482964999469772_n_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2370000%2F2370559%2F61858897_351734252193627_1680482964999469772_n_1024.jpg&h=19f4ae7a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://topick.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2370000/2370559/61249718_1231442277033056_9053324781463431559_n_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2370000%2F2370559%2F61249718_1231442277033056_9053324781463431559_n_1024.jpg&h=9e6d7c94&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2370559/%E9%84%AD%E8%A3%95%E7%8E%B2%E5%90%91%E6%94%9D%E5%BD%B1%E5%A4%A7%E5%B8%AB%E9%99%B8%E6%B0%B8%E5%8F%96%E7%B6%93%E5%AD%B8%E5%BD%B1%E7%9B%B8%E3%80%80%E7%85%A7%E7%89%87%E5%A4%B1%E7%84%A6Do%E5%A7%90%E6%8F%B6%E6%8F%84%EF%BC%9AFocus%E8%A6%81%E6%94%BE%E5%BE%8C%E9%9D%A2?mtc=10012\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2370559%2F%25E9%2584%25AD%25E8%25A3%2595%25E7%258E%25B2%25E5%2590%2591%25E6%2594%259D%25E5%25BD%25B1%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25B8%25AB%25E9%2599%25B8%25E6%25B0%25B8%25E5%258F%2596%25E7%25B6%2593%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E5%25BD%25B1%25E7%259B%25B8%25E3%2580%2580%25E7%2585%25A7%25E7%2589%2587%25E5%25A4%25B1%25E7%2584%25A6Do%25E5%25A7%2590%25E6%258F%25B6%25E6%258F%2584%25EF%25BC%259AFocus%25E8%25A6%2581%25E6%2594%25BE%25E5%25BE%258C%25E9%259D%25A2%3Fmtc%3D10012&d=M59wMjr1KB2wSFKn0iQ%2BgsTiFwqRwBg1VWT7Je45URE%3D&h=912d868d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2370559/%E9%84%AD%E8%A3%95%E7%8E%B2%E5%90%91%E6%94%9D%E5%BD%B1%E5%A4%A7%E5%B8%AB%E9%99%B8%E6%B0%B8%E5%8F%96%E7%B6%93%E5%AD%B8%E5%BD%B1%E7%9B%B8%E3%80%80%E7%85%A7%E7%89%87%E5%A4%B1%E7%84%A6Do%E5%A7%90%E6%8F%B6%E6%8F%84%EF%BC%9AFocus%E8%A6%81%E6%94%BE%E5%BE%8C%E9%9D%A2?mtc=10012</a>"},{"pid":"ce2f4c5375dec1d9b54a2139f3d4d9510b84d6f1","tid":1188282,"uid":134012,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T07:11:48.000Z","msg":"Mj"},{"pid":"8d01360a06827e3f2eb39fb2b17b8c6a46e0facd","ti